HEADWORD: Foredispose
<hw>Fore`dis*pose"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To bestow
beforehand.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>King James had by promise <qex>foredisposed</qex> the place on the
Bishop of Meath.</q> <rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Foredoom</ent>⟦br⟧
